channel.title: My 4 year birthday here
channel.description:
Well I registered on August 06, 2006, 09:42:37 PM. I've been here for more than 4 years now! It seems like no time at all. I'm a little late, however, It's good to see that the community has survived this long. I'm glad to be a member.
~Play Runescape, not the drug~
